            "content_license": "CC BY-SA 3.0",
            "score": 0,
            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1475259444,
            "creation_date": 1475259444,
            "body": "<p>Actually it doesn't work in the latest update of java 8. You can call it a bug fix according to them, but as far as I believe on my current knowledge this can't be called as a bug fix because it also lead to few conceptual changes too in java programming.<\/p>\n",
